        {
            "title": "聯想控股以27.17億元人幣售東航物流11.29%股份 料獲稅前收益2.97億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">聯想控股(03396)公布，與中國物流資本達成協議，將所持11.29%東航物流(601156.SH)股份售予對方，作價27.17億元(人民幣．下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"聯想控股官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/03396-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"聯想控股官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/03396-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">聯想控股官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">交易作價相等於東航物流每股15.156元，較該股昨天收市價17.42元折讓13%。交易完成後，聯想控股將不再持有東航物流股份。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">聯想控股預期，交易將確認稅前收益約2.97億元，套現所得淨額擬用於日常營運及償還債務。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司表示，投資東航物流股份已近10年，雙方在戰略與業務、公司治理方面展開諸多合作，今次出售將為東航物流引入新的長期戰略投資者，有利於對方在新一輪戰略周期中拓展境內外更多領域佈局，能夠進一步加強聯想控股、東航物流與新進股東之間戰略與業務協同。出售事項亦將增強聯想控股流動性水平及營運資金，有利於鞏固公司財務及現金狀況。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850234-%e8%81%af%e6%83%b3%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%a527-17%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e5%94%ae%e6%9d%b1%e8%88%aa%e7%89%a9%e6%b5%8111-29%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd-%e6%96%99%e7%8d%b2%e7%a8%85%e5%89%8d%e6%94%b6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/03396-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 08:48:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "領展以2.5億坡元售新加坡零售物業 作價較帳面估值有溢價",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">領展(00823)昨天公布，已訂立協議將新加坡零售物業 Swing By @ Thomson Plaza出售，作價2.5億坡元，較物業帳面估值有溢價。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：領展官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250513_FI_source-web_00823-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：領展官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250513_FI_source-web_00823-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：領展官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Swing By @ Thomson Plaza位於新加坡湯申(Thomson)社區Thomson Plaza的1樓及3樓，佔整個商場約56%的樓面面積，匯聚超過60個商戶。該物業最近一次的帳面估值是去年9月底時的2.026億坡元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今次領展出售上述物業作價2.5億坡元，較物業去年9月底時估值2.026億坡元溢價23.4%；較物業收購價1.725億坡元亦高出44.93%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">領展表示，今次交易屬公司持續推行資產組合優化策略的一部分，旨在於合適情況下進行資本循環，為基金單位持有人創造價值。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：領展官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250722_FI_source-web_00823-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：領展官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250722_FI_source-web_00823-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：領展官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">領展執行董事兼首席投資總裁宋俊彥表示，在領展繼續專注發揮亞太區零售商場核心優勢、並有意增加在新加坡投資比重同時，資產循環依然是領展積極優化資產組合策略中不可或缺的一環。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">他進一步指出，領展會定期檢視旗下資產，評估是否已最大程度發揮其短期價值，並在決定應否繼續持有時，以現價作為考量。這次出售令領展將資產增值的成果變現，並在資金超過短期需要的情況下，讓領展將資金回饋基金單位持有人。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850197-%e9%a0%98%e5%b1%95%e4%bb%a52-5%e5%84%84%e5%9d%a1%e5%85%83%e5%94%ae%e6%96%b0%e5%8a%a0%e5%9d%a1%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%ad-%e4%bd%9c%e5%83%b9%e8%bc%83%e5%b8%b3%e9%9d%a2%e4%bc%b0%e5%80%bc",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260409_FI_source-web_00823.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 08:35:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價急瀉逾13%至16%   跌穿100美元關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價昨日急挫，紐約期油及布蘭特期油俱跌穿每桶100美元關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5月紐約期油收報每桶94.41美元，大跌18.54美元，跌幅16.41%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6月倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶94.75美元，跌14.52美元，跌幅13.29%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場分析認為，美伊停火兩星期，市場期望霍爾木茲海峽重新開放，是導致油價急跌的主要原因。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15849996-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e6%80%a5%e7%80%89%e9%80%be13%e8%87%b316-%e8%b7%8c%e7%a9%bf100%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e9%97%9c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil_source-ap_-1-1-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 08:35:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期低水約50點 重磅港股ADR多半回吐",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時13分跌54點或0.21%，報25843點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報25854點，較香港上日現貨收市低38點或0.15%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣507.1元，較上日香港收市低0.86元或0.17%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣122.7元，較上日香港收市低3.83元或3.03%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣88.4元，較上日香港收市低0.09元或0.1%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣113.7元，較上日香港收市高1.84元或1.65%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣32.7元，較上日香港收市低0.1元或0.32%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣141.4元，較上日香港收市高2.78元或2.01%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣88.9元，較上日香港收市高0.21元或0.24%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣411.9元，較上日香港收市低0.49元或0.12%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣62.4元，較上日香港收市低0.03元或0.04%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.5元，較上日香港收市低0.01元或0.15%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報25859點，跌89點，較上日恒指收市25893點，低水34點。科指期貨夜市收報4928點，較上日科指收市高水5點；國指期貨夜市收報8656點，較上日國指收市低水21點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850183-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e7%b4%8450%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%a4%9a%e5%8d%8a%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 08:17:30",
