        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段回吐 日經暫微跌不足200點 韓指跌逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日韓股市經過昨天大幅反彈後，今早雙雙回吐，當中以韓股調整幅度較大。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260128_FI_source-ap_JP.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260128_FI_source-ap_JP.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時11分，南韓首爾綜合指數跌69點或1.19%，報5802點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日經平均指數暫則微跌159點或0.28%，報56204點。</p>\n</div>",
